00:35:57,970 --> 00:36:00,850
made me vomit blood, long after I've forgotten my name, my address,

586
00:36:00,860 --> 00:36:02,120
and what a car key is for, yeah.

587
00:36:02,130 --> 00:36:04,480
I think she's found something here besides justin,

