597
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:26,290
-No.
-Ok...if you're too scared.

598
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:30,110
She plays me like a piano!Wait.

599
00:36:30,130 --> 00:36:32,580
I'm surprised you haven't bricked up that hole yet.

600
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,670
I thought I might have to go back in there.

601
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:42,000
Have you ever thought about having a revolving door installed, maybe a turnstile?

602
00:36:55,690 --> 00:36:58,180
-What was that?
-Nothing.

603
00:37:03,660 --> 00:37:07,170
-Are we there yet?
-No, let's go.

604
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:30,110
Melinda.

605
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:33,290
-He's here.
-What?

606
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,390
You really shouldn't be here.

607
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,350
Neither should you.

608
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,200
-No, I belong here.
-No, you don'T.

609
00:37:38,210 --> 00:37:40,700
-They're just trying to make you think--
-it's really all right.

610
00:37:40,710 --> 00:37:42,380
There's so much I can do.

611
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,920
They're gonna teach me things here.

612
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:46,100
What things?

613
00:37:46,110 --> 00:37:49,600
You don't have to tell her anything.She's not welcome.

614
00:37:50,570 --> 00:37:52,690
-Julie's here.
-Oh, that's good.

615
00:37:52,700 --> 00:37:54,200
