639
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:09,770
They don't want what you have.

640
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:12,610
You have to go into the light.

641
00:39:14,100 --> 00:39:17,450
Melinda, I have no idea what's going on.Should I be scared?

642
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:24,280
Were you really going to kill me?

643
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:26,210
It crossed my mind.

644
00:39:27,100 --> 00:39:28,790
