648
00:39:39,430 --> 00:39:41,440
She's trying to make you angry.

649
00:39:41,950 --> 00:39:45,130
She wants you to hate her because that's how ghosts like her get stronger.

650
00:39:45,140 --> 00:39:46,620
Please don't let her do it.

651
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:51,150
It's ok.Really.

652
00:39:56,410 --> 00:40:00,470
