653
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:05,060
The way you made me feel like I had something to offer.

654
00:40:06,270 --> 00:40:09,650
I just never got a chance to offer to someone better than you.

655
00:40:11,930 --> 00:40:13,590
So thanks for that.

656
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:15,560
And for the rest of it.

657
00:40:19,210 --> 00:40:20,800
I forgive you.

658
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:25,820
And I forgive myself for leaving you there.

659
00:40:45,390 --> 00:40:47,400
I'm so proud of you.

660
00:40:50,110 --> 00:40:53,940
There's just one more thing you're gonna have to help me with.

661
00:40:55,800 --> 00:40:59,420
You know, it would be really cruel if you were lying about this.

662
00:40:59,430 --> 00:41:01,650
I'm not.I promise.

663
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,850
Justin's here with us.

664
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:09,870
I told him that you were in grandview and you wanted to say good-bye.

665
00:41:09,930 --> 00:41:11,450
And that I'm sorry.

666
00:41:11,970 --> 00:41:14,420
He also wanted to say that he was sorry.

667
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:17,110
Justin, if you're there...

668
00:41:17,540 --> 00:41:21,130
or here, sorry isn't good enough.

669
00:41:21,710 --> 00:41:24,500
